// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-1555 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: c0e1a430-0fcf-5648-ad3b-5920005553da

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:22.04*")
